data.description: Property combines modern design with a cozy and welcoming atmosphere.  An attractive two car garage, adding to its curb appeal.  Inside, you will discover a well-designed interior with a spacious and open layout.  The living area is bright and inviting, providing an excellent space for relaxation and gatherings.  The kitchen is equipped with contemporary appliances, stylish cabinetry, and ample counter space, making it a dream for home cooks.  This property features multiple bedrooms, offering flexibility and comfort for a family or individuals.  The master suite is a private retreat with its own bathroom and ample closet space.  The backyard provides a great outdoor space for leisure and activities.  Highly desirable, providing easy access to schools, shopping, dining and recreational opportunities.
